1. Healthcare (Patient Appointment Reminder)

“Write a simple message reminding a patient about their appointment tomorrow at 10 AM.”

Prompt :
Role: You are a Nurse at Kaiser Permanente.
Goal: Remind the patient about his appointment tomorrow at 10 AM.
Audience: Male patient between 30–40 years old.
Channel: SMS message.
Tone: Professional, friendly.
Format: Max 50 words.
Constraints: No medical details; keep simple; add a clear CTA.
Task: Draft 2 variations.
Few-Shot Examples:
Example 1: “Hi Mike, this is a reminder about your appointment tomorrow at 10 AM. Please arrive 10 minutes early.”
  

